            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-lg text-slate-900 group-hover:text-yellow-600 transition">
                ğŸ‘‘ Featured Listing - $99/month
              </span>
              <p class="text-slate-700 text-sm mt-1">
                Get premium placement, gold badge, and 3x more visibility in search results
